e:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">This submission has sought to demonstrate that:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 64.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">The favoured </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">options for domestic heat are undermined by the UK</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">’</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">s </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">current</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> reliance on the burning of fossil fuel for</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">electricity generation. Until electricity is decarbonised, which</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> is unlikely within</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> the time frame of </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">the RHI scheme</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline"> the current proposals could INCREASE carbon emissions from homes</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline"> now using oil</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">.</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">  </span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 64.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">B30K Bio liquid is available as a direct replacement fuel for homes</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">now on oil. </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">This </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">offers </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">a </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">low capital cost for exis</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">ting appliance modification, comparable heat output and boiler efficiency, reliability, and has no impact on the nation’s electricity supply infrastructure.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 64.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">The DECC Heat Strategy needs to be amended </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">to incentivi</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">s</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">e</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline"> a “Balanced T</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">ransition” </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">approach to de-c</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">arbonising heat</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">;</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 72pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 64.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Government policy to encourage take-up of renewable heat by home owners is over optimistic and </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">does not take into account </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">reluctance of people to switch to unproven technologies</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">;</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline"> and,</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 64.06pt; padding-left:7.94pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">The domestic RHI should be amended to allow </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">bio-liquids (B</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">30K) to be eligible for support, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">and this fuel could make a significant contribution to carbon emission reductions.</span></li></ul><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">25.</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">OFTEC thanks the Committee for this opportunity to submit evidence and is prepared to appear before the committee to give</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> oral evidence</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">August 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:9pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:5pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>